 \underbrace{\idotsint}_{n}  \exp\left(-\sum_{1\le i\le j\le n}^n x_i x_j\right) \mathrm{d}x_1\cdots\mathrm{d}x_n  
x^T=(x_1,\ldots,x_n)
A
n\times n
\int\ldots\int_{\mathbb{R}^n}\exp\left\{-\frac12 x^TAx\right\}dx_1\ldots dx_n=\frac{(2\pi)^{n/2}}{\sqrt{\mathrm{det}\,A}},\tag{1}
 A=-\frac12\left( \begin{array}{ccccc} 2&1&1&\cdots&1\\ 1&2&1&\cdots&1\\ 1&1&2&\cdots&1\\ \vdots&\vdots&\vdots&\ddots&\vdots\\ 1&1&1&\cdots&2 \end{array}\right)? 
